decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color:=
 #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Howey test</=
a>=E2=80=9D says that something is a security if =E2=80=9Cthere is the inve=
stment of money in a common enterprise with a reasonable expectation of pro=
fits to be derived from the efforts of others.=E2=80=9D The test comes from=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24514165.265021/a=
HR0cHM6Ly9zdXByZW1lLmp1c3RpYS5jb20vY2FzZXMvZmVkZXJhbC91cy8zMjgvMjkzLw/607f0=
